<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA19">
<l>araṉeṉkō nāṉmuka ṉeṉkō variya</l>
<l>paraṉeṉkō paṇpuṇara māṭṭēṉ - muraṇaḻiyat</l>
<l>tāṉavaṉaip pātat taṉiviralāṟ ceṟṟāṉai</l>
<l>yāṉavaṉai yemmāṉai yiṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will I say “Hara”? Will I say “the four-faced one”? will I say</l>
<l>“the rare Highest one”? I cannot perceive [his] qualities.</l>
<l>– to the one who destroyed with a single toe of [his] foot the Dhānava</l> 
<l>so that [his] opposition perished, him who is our lord today.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
